f\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f4fbc637ec2cdd2794a4d98177b7be5226b8fad","tid":463200,"uid":65074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T10:52:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n河南90後富二代薛某，自中學起追求心儀女生8年均不獲應允。今年3月他聽到女方聲稱要跟別人交往，從19樓扔她下樓致死，其後向警方自首表示願意民事陪償。杭州中級人民法院近日審結案件，形容事件性質太過惡劣，就算被告自首仍不足以減輕罪責，判處薛某死刑。死者母親聞訊激動得暈倒，她的親戚指，她一心想要的，就是這個結果<br />\n<br />\n(錢江晚報 / 澎湃新聞)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171109/s00004/1510216330318\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171109%2Fs00004%2F1510216330318&d=qFMizAWkK58qCn8pkwBdHUkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=398c1d09\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171109%2Fs00004%2F1510216330318&h=caf0224f\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171109/s00004/1510216330318</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咪講左想一命填一命多過要錢lor<br />\n上面班撚樣嘈乜9"},{"pid":"a0c562d30808c77c099e763dd2e683767895a841","tid":463200,"uid":82482,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T10:53:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>警世,教訓你班女人唔好收兵收得咁盡</blockquote><br />\n警世係因為有錢都唔識利用<br />\n<br />\n有錢驚無女？"},{"pid":"893499846915a301080c0d77ea0697eec3057682","tid":463200,"uid":83060,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T10:55:31.000Z","msg":"應該係咁，係港女比啲毒撚寵壞哂。"},{"pid":"f69123b1292cc55f1d70fac093dfa03764116325","tid":463200,"uid":64155,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T11:02:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>毒撚好恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你件臭閪好好?"},{"pid":"0271ea956cc582fe079484dc75f4df3fc5c625b6","tid":463200,"uid":143454,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T11:12:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}